      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，验证失败就直接结束。但验证通过的话，要先查缓存，这个节点叫CacheGet，同样用HIPAA_Vault来标注安全级别。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CacheGet",
        "YES",
        "NO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了：ReqValid分出YES和NO两条支路，NO直接到END，YES连到CacheGet。下一步是缓存命中判断？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Found",
        "miss"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，CacheGet后面加一个Found判断，还是由EMR_Sync来处理。命中失败走miss分支，进入缓存空间检查CacheHasSpace。",
      "elements_involved": [
